{"snp5.2:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 5.2 ","snp5.2:0.2":"Ajitamanavapuccha ","snp5.2:1.1":"“Kenassu nivuto loko, ","snp5.2:1.2":"(iccayasma ajito) ","snp5.2:1.3":"Kenassu nappakasati; ","snp5.2:1.4":"Kissabhilepanam brusi, ","snp5.2:1.5":"Kimsu tassa mahabbhayam”. ","snp5.2:2.1":"“Avijjaya nivuto loko, ","snp5.2:2.2":"(ajitati bhagava) ","snp5.2:2.3":"Veviccha pamada nappakasati; ","snp5.2:2.4":"Jappabhilepanam brumi, ","snp5.2:2.5":"Dukkhamassa mahabbhayam”. ","snp5.2:3.1":"“Savanti sabbadhi sota, ","snp5.2:3.2":"(iccayasma ajito) ","snp5.2:3.3":"Sotanam kim nivaranam; ","snp5.2:3.4":"Sotanam samvaram bruhi, ","snp5.2:3.5":"Kena sota pidhiyyare”. ","snp5.2:4.1":"“Yani sotani lokasmim, ","snp5.2:4.2":"(ajitati bhagava) ","snp5.2:4.3":"Sati tesam nivaranam; ","snp5.2:4.4":"Sotanam samvaram brumi, ","snp5.2:4.5":"Pannayete pidhiyyare”. ","snp5.2:5.1":"“Panna ceva sati yanca, ","snp5.2:5.2":"(iccayasma ajito) ","snp5.2:5.3":"Namarupanca marisa; ","snp5.2:5.4":"Etam me puttho pabruhi, ","snp5.2:5.5":"Katthetam uparujjhati”. ","snp5.2:6.1":"“Yametam panham apucchi, ","snp5.2:6.2":"ajita tam vadami te; ","snp5.2:6.3":"Yattha namanca rupanca, ","snp5.2:6.4":"asesam uparujjhati; ","snp5.2:6.5":"Vinnanassa nirodhena, ","snp5.2:6.6":"etthetam uparujjhati”. ","snp5.2:7.1":"“Ye ca sankhatadhammase, ","snp5.2:7.2":"ye ca sekha puthu idha; ","snp5.2:7.3":"Tesam me nipako iriyam, ","snp5.2:7.4":"puttho pabruhi marisa”. ","snp5.2:8.1":"“Kamesu nabhigijjheyya, ","snp5.2:8.2":"Manasanavilo siya; ","snp5.2:8.3":"Kusalo sabbadhammanam, ","snp5.2:8.4":"Sato bhikkhu paribbaje”ti. ","snp5.2:8.5":"Ajitamanavapuccha pathama. "}